dataObject.content: Greta Thunberg, the teenage climate activist from Sweden, the 16-year-old’s steely-eyed courage has helped inspire kids across the country — and the world — to join her call to strike from school last week and stand up for more aggressive action to combat the climate crisis.

annotationData.content: {"category":{"label":"Biased"},"rationale":"Biased, the person who wrote it clearly agrees with the cause. Using terms such as courage, inspiring, shows a personal interest in the movement. "}
